title: Chinese Soy Pork & Ginger Rice Congee Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Tender, sweet soy pork rests atop a silky ginger rice congee, offering a comforting blend of savoury and aromatic flavors. Finished with a drizzle of garlic chilli oil and crispy shallots, this dish delivers a satisfying kick with every spoonful.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
